        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Strengthening the Office of Personnel Management Act</b></p> <p>This bill provides statutory authority for the mission of the Office of Personnel Management (OPM), establishes the Chief Management Officer and the OPM Advisory Committee on Human Capital Management, and specifies additional requirements for the appointment of the OPM Director and the removal of the OPM Director or Deputy Director.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
